Title: Self-Duality and the KdV Hierarchy

Authors: Ashok Das and C.A.P. Galvao

Comments: 7 pages

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A8 (1993) 661-666

We derive the entire KdV hierarchy as well as the recursion relations fromthe self-duality condition on gauge fields in four dimensions.